-# frozen_string_literal: true
%p
  As requested, here is a list of Keygen accounts that this email address is associated with:
%ul
  - @users.each do |user|
    %li
      %strong Account name:
      %span= user.account.name
      %br
      %strong Unique ID:
      %span= user.account.slug
      %br
      %span
        %strong Recover:
        %a(href="https://app.keygen.sh/recover/password?account=#{user.account.slug}&email=#{user.email}")
          click here
      %br
      %span
        %strong Login:
        %a(href="https://app.keygen.sh/login?account=#{user.account.slug}")
          click here
%p
  Let us know if you have any questions, or if you are still having trouble logging in.
